286
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:49,320
Since Youzhi has business with Godfather,

287
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:50,800
your daughter will not disturb you.

288
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:53,440
Youzhi.

289
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:55,360
See your Sister Hua out.

290
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:56,080
Yes.

291
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:03,480
Sister, why are you so happy?

292
00:16:03,680 --> 00:16:04,880
Sister is getting married.

293
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:05,840
Naturally, I am happy.

294
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:08,040
Which family's young master is so lucky?

295
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:12,600
It is a fool who only favors me.

296
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:15,440
Even if I have a thousand charms,

297
00:16:16,040 --> 00:16:17,320
to whom can I tell them?

298
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:20,360
So the person she wants to marry

299
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:23,120
is not Wang Zhi.

300
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:24,560
Youzhi.

301
00:16:24,920 --> 00:16:25,960
If you keep looking at me,

302
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:28,320
Lord Li will really lose his life.

303
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:30,800
Move aside.

304
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:32,800
Tonight the moon is full.

305
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:35,320
Dreaming back to the capital.

306
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:38,200
To show my ambition with death.

307
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:40,000
Only then can I make up for...

308
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,480
A scholar,

309
00:16:43,400 --> 00:16:45,120
what he seeks in a lifetime...

310
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:48,160
Enough.

311
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:57,120
Lord Li.

312
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:58,480
Now that you want to die,

313
00:16:58,480 --> 00:16:59,360
it won't be that easy.

314
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:04,760
Tonight the moon is full.

315
00:17:06,080 --> 00:17:07,440
The whole world knows.

316
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:28,520
Tonight business is busy.

317
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:30,160
We must go early

318
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:31,240
to assist His Majesty.

319
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:31,720
Yes.

320
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:33,760
The 18th year of the Chenghua reign.

321
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:35,960
The Eastern Depot and Embroidered Uniform Guard jointly

322
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:37,400
collected evidence of the Western Depot's

323
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:39,360
various unjust cases over the past five years.

324
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:41,520
Using the Depot's power to frame dissidents

325
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:42,640
and persecute loyal officials.

326
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:43,840
The evidence is conclusive.

327
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:46,320
The Emperor was furious upon receiving the memorial.

328
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:48,560
He ordered the temporary withdrawal of the Western Depot,

329
00:17:49,120 --> 00:17:50,040
the disbanding of its personnel,

330
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:51,760
the deposition of Eunuch Lord Wang Zhi,

331
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:53,440
and his confinement in his manor

332
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:54,760
to await sentencing.

333
00:18:08,320 --> 00:18:09,240
Thinking back,

334
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:12,200
I also once saw His Majesty at this age.

335
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:38,240
Noble Consort.

336
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:39,600
Well?

337
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:41,600
Reporting to Noble Consort.

338
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:42,840
In today's morning court,

339
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:44,480
the court ministers jointly petitioned

340
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:46,280
demanding a thorough investigation into the Western Depot's affairs

341
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:47,720
and the abolition of the Western Depot.

342
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:51,480
How did His Majesty react?

343
00:18:52,040 --> 00:18:53,440
His Majesty sympathizes with you, Noble Consort.

344
00:18:53,720 --> 00:18:54,480
He only ordered

345
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:56,320
Director-in-chief Wang to be confined in his manor

346
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:57,480
to await interrogation and sentencing.

347
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:02,320
I knew it.

348
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:05,200
That hypocritical whore from Blossom Pavilion three years ago

349
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:06,400
was uncharacteristically docile.

350
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:08,760
Turns out she was waiting here to settle scores with Wang Zhi.

351
00:19:10,600 --> 00:19:12,200
Help me remove my jewelry and makeup.

352
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:13,640
When His Majesty comes,

353
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:15,960
no one is allowed to mention the Western Depot.

354
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:30,840
How did they agree to let you in?

355
00:19:34,800 --> 00:19:35,520
I forgot.

356
00:19:36,760 --> 00:19:38,840
Without the Western Depot's backing,

357
00:19:39,360 --> 00:19:40,280
Blossom Pavilion...

358
00:19:40,560 --> 00:19:42,040
still has the Eastern Depot.

359
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:43,960
No need to look.

360
00:19:44,840 --> 00:19:47,000
Want to see me looking like a defeated dog?

361
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:48,800
You came too early.

362
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:51,360
You should have come in a few days.

363
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:55,360
You really have everything clearly arranged.

364
00:19:58,360 --> 00:19:59,400
How could I?

365
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:02,840
I never expected...

366
00:20:03,320 --> 00:20:04,640
that you would throw away our twenty-plus years

367
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:05,840
of childhood affection

368
00:20:05,840 --> 00:20:07,160
completely and utterly.

369
00:20:12,280 --> 00:20:13,560
The word "affection"

370
00:20:16,080 --> 00:20:18,320
cannot be measured by time.

371
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:20,560
When was it?

372
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:23,000
How did you plan this?

373
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,040
Three years ago.

374
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:29,480
It really was for that fool from the Divine Machine Battalion.

375
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:30,440
You are not worthy to mention him.

376
00:20:52,120 --> 00:20:52,760
Enough.

377
00:20:54,560 --> 00:20:56,040
I was blinded for a moment.

378
00:20:57,360 --> 00:20:58,080
That's right.

379
00:20:58,280 --> 00:21:00,280
Someone as clean as Lin Feng

380
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:03,080
belongs in the Pure Land.

381
00:21:04,360 --> 00:21:05,200
While you and I

382
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:08,240
only deserve the Avici Hell.

383
00:21:09,520 --> 00:21:11,280
You don't deserve to see him again either.

384
00:21:12,320 --> 00:21:13,000
Yes.

385
00:21:15,760 --> 00:21:16,800
I naively thought

386
00:21:16,800 --> 00:21:18,480
I had a chance to become clean.

387
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:23,640
But in the end, I still got him killed.

388
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:29,280
Shuoyue.

389
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,160
With your intellect,

390
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:35,000
you could never have planned this so meticulously.

391
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:38,560
The person planning behind you...

392
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:40,520
is Shang Hua, isn't it?

393
00:22:25,520 --> 00:22:25,920
All right.

394
00:22:26,640 --> 00:22:27,280
Come, Lord Shen.

395
00:22:27,600 --> 00:22:28,320
Come over and help me take a look.

396
00:22:29,600 --> 00:22:30,920
"Flowers flying freely,"

397
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:32,280
"light as a dream."

398
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:34,680
Willow catkins without hallucinogens

399
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:36,160
are already so elusive.

400
00:22:36,800 --> 00:22:37,520
With them added,

401
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:39,280
they become even more elusive.

402
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:41,320
A weightless falsehood.

403
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:44,320
If Lord Shen can't be bothered to look,

404
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:46,240
you could at least help me check for errors.

405
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:49,120
After all, Lord Shen is much more learned than I am.

406
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:49,760
Come, come, come.

407
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:50,360
Help me out.

408
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:54,200
But having said that,

409
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:56,400
with the sudden political upheaval in court,

410
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:57,480
the Eunuch Lords

411
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:58,720
probably won't have time for us.

412
00:23:01,520 --> 00:23:03,560
With Vice Minister Zhang's talents, you're bound to succeed.

413
00:23:04,120 --> 00:23:05,360
Why didn't you join the Embroidered Uniform Guard back then

414
00:23:05,360 --> 00:23:06,120
to showcase your skills?

415
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:09,000
Ever since I returned from the battlefield,

416
00:23:09,280 --> 00:23:10,120
I've figured it out.

417
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:11,560
In this life,

418
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:12,440
one should enjoy the moment.

419
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,480
Life and death are fated.

420
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:15,000
I should just properly

421
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:17,080
enjoy this land of tenderness and riches.

422
00:23:17,280 --> 00:23:17,920
Don't you agree?

423
00:23:18,600 --> 00:23:19,240
By the way,

424
00:23:19,800 --> 00:23:21,280
why haven't I seen Battalion Commander Yuan today?

425
00:23:21,320 --> 00:23:22,480
He has a youthful temperament.

426
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:25,160
Whenever something big like this happens,

427
00:23:25,520 --> 00:23:26,960
he calls in sick to recover at home,

428
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:28,920
avoiding the conflict for a few months.

429
00:23:30,520 --> 00:23:31,800
That kid really has it figured out, doesn't he?

430
00:23:31,840 --> 00:23:32,480
That's the way to be.

431
00:23:33,120 --> 00:23:34,600
Why push yourself so hard?

432
00:23:34,800 --> 00:23:35,320
Right?

433
00:23:36,840 --> 00:23:37,760
Otherwise, today,

434
00:23:38,080 --> 00:23:39,440
why don't you come with me to Blossom Pavilion?

435
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:40,600
Tell me,

436
00:23:40,800 --> 00:23:41,840
what kind of women do you like?

437
00:23:42,840 --> 00:23:43,720
Like?

438
00:23:45,080 --> 00:23:46,360
What does it matter if I like someone?

439
00:23:47,800 --> 00:23:48,760
What I like

440
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:52,600
has never been for me to decide.

441
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:55,120
I'd only end up harming them.

442
00:23:59,040 --> 00:24:00,200
It's not easy for Lord Shen either.

443
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:02,120
Well, I'm going to go have fun.

444
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:03,400
Please suit yourself, Lord Shen.

445
00:24:12,320 --> 00:24:13,080
Vice Minister Zhang.

446
00:24:14,320 --> 00:24:14,760
What is it?

447
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:15,920
Regretting it?

448
00:24:16,280 --> 00:24:17,480
Want to come to Blossom Pavilion with me?

449
00:24:18,800 --> 00:24:19,680
At Blossom Pavilion,

450
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:22,120
there's no girl like Tang Xi to tease you.

451
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:24,880
Lord Shen, you've gone bad.

452
00:24:48,840 --> 00:24:50,840
Now that Eunuch Lord Wang is under house arrest,

453
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:52,400
what is the use of you spying on us?

454
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:53,520
As a Hidden Guard,

455
00:24:53,800 --> 00:24:55,440
if you haven't received new orders from your master,

456
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:57,400
you are not allowed to leave your post.

457
00:24:57,800 --> 00:24:59,000
You may leave now.

458
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:00,360
The Eastern Depot

459
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:03,800
will never give the Western Depot a chance to recover.

460
00:25:05,360 --> 00:25:07,440
My family does not allow me to betray my master.

461
00:25:08,520 --> 00:25:09,840
Otherwise, their deal with the master

462
00:25:09,840 --> 00:25:10,560
would come to an end.

463
00:25:12,080 --> 00:25:13,120
There are always so many people

464
00:25:13,120 --> 00:25:14,200
living for the sake of others.

465
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:18,320
Zhang Yi still lives freely and at ease.

466
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:20,360
In my view,

467
00:25:20,360 --> 00:25:21,680
Zhang Yi isn't all that free.

468
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:23,760
His life is even somewhat heavy.

469
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:29,040
These are the household registration dossiers for him and you.

470
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:34,600
The two of you are actually quite alike.

471
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:36,200
You just chose different paths.

472
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:43,200
Zhang Yi

473
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,000
was once of lowly status.

474
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,760
He was raised by prostitutes.

475
00:25:48,080 --> 00:25:48,760
Relying on prostitutes

476
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:51,320
using money from their trade to clear the registry,

477
00:25:51,960 --> 00:25:53,000
changing it to respectable status.

478
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:55,920
Then joining the army with that respectable status,

479
00:25:56,440 --> 00:25:57,560
repeatedly achieving military merits,

480
00:25:58,040 --> 00:25:59,160
and performing outstandingly,

481
00:25:59,800 --> 00:26:01,880
he applied for a transfer to the Divine Machine Battalion.

482
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:03,280
Those aunties of yours

483
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:05,240
have long since been reborn into good families.

484
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,400
It's not good for you to keep coming here.

485
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:09,040
Otherwise, why has it been three years

486
00:26:09,120 --> 00:26:10,320
with no sign of a promotion yet?

487
00:26:10,320 --> 00:26:11,000
It doesn't matter.

488
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,360
As long as the aunties are living well.

489
00:26:12,760 --> 00:26:13,560
I'm going to see Auntie Wang.

490
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:14,360
You guys keep busy.

491
00:26:20,040 --> 00:26:20,520
This is cooked.

492
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:21,280
It's ready to eat.

493
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:22,840
Litigator Lu,

494
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:24,920
regarding our case of hijacking Li Chenyang,

495
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:25,960
will it end just like this?

496
00:26:28,120 --> 00:26:29,000
Lady Hua said

497
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,720
it shouldn't be a big problem.

498
00:26:31,040 --> 00:26:32,240
If the truth of

499
00:26:32,760 --> 00:26:33,760
Li Chenyang's case

500
00:26:34,520 --> 00:26:35,240
is made public,

501
00:26:35,800 --> 00:26:36,960
the Eastern and Western Depots

502
00:26:37,360 --> 00:26:39,280
will surely fight to the death.

503
00:26:39,280 --> 00:26:40,080
There will be no room for compromise.

504
00:26:41,080 --> 00:26:42,640
As for the closing statement,

505
00:26:43,480 --> 00:26:45,040
that's all just lying through their teeth.

506
00:26:45,320 --> 00:26:46,240
It shouldn't be a major issue.

507
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:47,960
Then will Lord Li...

508
00:26:48,040 --> 00:26:49,080
Lord Li's life

509
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:50,400
depends entirely on his own luck.

510
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,000
I have ordered the Tang Clan members

511
00:26:52,080 --> 00:26:53,440
to protect his family for five years.

512
00:26:54,040 --> 00:26:54,880
All outcomes

513
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:56,240
need not be guessed at this moment.

514
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:58,080
Let us watch and see how things change.

515
00:27:04,280 --> 00:27:05,400
It's broad daylight.

516
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:07,280
Why is the brothel so lively?

517
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,640
They're open for business.

518
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:11,600
You can't forbid people from daytime indulgence.

519
00:27:13,120 --> 00:27:15,600
So young, yet so vulgar.

520
00:27:16,600 --> 00:27:17,600
I'm vulgar?

521
00:27:18,440 --> 00:27:19,960
Would a vulgar person use the Imperial Sword...

522
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:20,720
...to slice meat for you just now?

523
00:27:21,280 --> 00:27:22,480
That's not being vulgar.

524
00:27:22,880 --> 00:27:24,880
It's a reckless waste of a treasure.

525
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:26,640
Enough.

526
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:29,440
You still have the leisure to bicker.

527
00:27:29,800 --> 00:27:30,640
Lady Hua said...

528
00:27:30,800 --> 00:27:31,600
...that the four of us...

529
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:33,160
...are to wait here for the leader of The Four Directions.

530
00:27:33,560 --> 00:27:34,440
Look at yourselves.

531
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:35,200
Where are your manners?

532
00:27:35,320 --> 00:27:36,040
All you do is eat.

533
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:37,760
Young Master Tang.

534
00:27:38,120 --> 00:27:39,160
I really must have a word with you.

535
00:27:41,320 --> 00:27:42,880
I prefer the lamb neck fillet.

536
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:46,720
Litigator Lu.

537
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:49,120
That sounded quite affectionate.

538
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:51,920
Who says The Four Directions answers to one person?

539
00:27:52,600 --> 00:27:54,680
Without me, the number one swordsman Tang Xi...

540
00:28:00,520 --> 00:28:01,040
Young Master Tang.

541
00:28:01,520 --> 00:28:03,760
You can't publicly attack a fourth-rank official.

542
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:06,120
If you don't tell...

543
00:28:06,800 --> 00:28:07,600
...where is the "public"?

544
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:09,440
If you put it that way...

545
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:10,880
...if I were to molest you in public...

546
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:11,520
...and they don't say a word...

547
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:12,760
...it wouldn't count as molestation.

548
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:14,840
Lord Zhang.

549
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:16,720
Coming to Blossom Pavilion today...

550
00:28:17,600 --> 00:28:18,880
...is it to eat meat...

551
00:28:19,480 --> 00:28:20,440
...or to handle a case?

552
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:21,520
What do you think?

553
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:22,960
Lord Zhang.

554
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:25,520
I suggest you let go of our little lunatic.

555
00:28:26,040 --> 00:28:28,200
Or I'll strangle you with this thread.

556
00:28:29,840 --> 00:28:30,560
Lord Zhang.

557
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:32,040
You're late.

558
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,200
You betrayed us.

559
00:28:37,840 --> 00:28:38,920
Haven't you always wanted to meet...

560
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:40,600
...the true mastermind of The Four Directions?

561
00:28:41,360 --> 00:28:42,760
You've been pen pals with him for a year...

562
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:43,880
...and you didn't realize?

563
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:48,360
So now...

564
00:28:48,360 --> 00:28:49,520
...allow me to introduce myself.

565
00:28:50,600 --> 00:28:51,200
I am...

566
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:52,760
Grand Court of Justice Vice Minister, Zhang Yi.

567
